  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the feasibility of modified Constraint-Induced Aphasia
      Therapy (CIAT) in the early sub-acute stage and to examine the efficacy of modified CIAT
      versus standard treatment with the same intensity of intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
